    "Content": "```toml\n[rss]\nurls = [\"RSS订阅链接\"]\n\n[openlist]\nurl = \"http://localhost:5244\"       # Openlist 访问地址\ntoken = \"\"                          # 令牌，见「设置 → 其他 → 令牌」\ndownload_path = \"/PikPak/Anime\"     # 下载保存路径\noffline_download_tool = \"QBITTORRENT\"  # 离线下载工具\n\n[llm]\nopenai_api_key = \"\"                 # API Key\nopenai_base_url = \"https://api.deepseek.com/v1\"\nopenai_model = \"deepseek-chat\"\n```",
